quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  6,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  6,1,har terhan ki tareef khuda hi ko sazawar hai jis ne asmano aur zameen ko pedakiya aur andhera aur roshni banai phir bhi kafir ( aur cheezon ko ) khuda ke barabar tehrate hain
  6,2,wohi to hai jis ne tum ko matti se pedakiya phir ( marnay ka ) aik waqt muqarrar kar diya aur aik muddat is ke haan aur muqarrar hai phir bhi tum ( ae kafroo khuda ke baray mein ) shak karte ho
  6,3,aur asmano aur zameen mein wohi ( aik ) khuda hai tumhari posheeda aur zahir sab baatein jaanta hai aur tum jo amal karte ho sab se waaqif hai
  6,4,aur khuda ki nishanion mein se koi nishani un logon ke paas nahi aati magar yeh is se munh phair letay hain
  6,5,jab un ke paas haq aaya to is ko bhi jhutla diya so un ko un cheezon ka jin se yeh istehza karte hain anqareeb injaam maloom ho jaye ga
  6,6,kiya unhon ne nahi dekha ke hum ne un se pehlay kitni amton ko halaak kar diya jin ke paon malik mein aisay jama diye they ke tumahray paon bhi aisay nahi jamaye aur un par aasman se lagataar meen barsaya aur nehrein bana den jo un ke ( makanon ke ) neechay beh rahi theen phir un ko un ke gunaaho ke sabab halaak kar diya aur un ke baad aur ummatain peda kar den
  6,7,aur agar hum tum par kaaghzon par likhi hui kitaab nazil karte aur yeh usay apne hathon se bhi tatole letay to jo kafir hain woh yahi keh dete ke yeh to ( saaf aur ) Sarih jaadoo hai
  6,8,aur kehte hain ke un ( paighambar ) par farishta kyun nazil nah howa ( jo un ki tasdeeq karta ) agar hum farishta nazil karte to kaam hi Faisal ho jata phir unhein ( mutlaq ) mohlat nah di jati
  6,9,neez agar hum kisi farishta ko bhaijtay to usay mard ki soorat mein bhaijtay aur jo shuba ( ab ) karte hain isi shay mein phir inhen daal dete
  6,10,aur tum se pehlay bhi payghambaroon ke sath tamaskhur hotay rahay hain so jo log un mein se tamaskhurkiya karte they un ko tamaskhur ki saza ne aa ghera ا
  6,11,kaho ke ( ae munkareen risalat ) malik mein chalo phiro phir dekho ke jhutlanay walon kakiya injaam howa
  6,12,( un se ) pucho ke aasman aur zameen mein jo kuch hai kis ka hai keh do khuda ka is ne apni zaat ( pak ) par rehmat ko lazim kar liya hai woh tum sab ko qayamat ke din jis mein kuch bhi shak nahi zaroor jama kere ga jin logon ne apne aap ko nuqsaan mein daal rakha hai woh imaan nahi laatay
  6,13,aur jo makhlooq raat aur din mein bastii hai sab isi ki hai aur woh santa jaanta hai
  6,14,kahokiya mein khuda ko chore kar kisi aur ko madadgaar bunun ke ( wohi to ) asmano aur zameen ka peda karne wala hai aur wohi ( sab ko ) khana deta hai aur khud kisi se khana nahi laita ( yeh bhi ) keh do ke mujhe yeh hukum howa hai ke mein sab se pehlay islam laane wala hon aur yeh ke tum ( ae paighambar! ) mushrikon mein nah hona
  6,15,( yeh bhi ) keh do ke agar mein apne perwar-digaar ki nafarmani karoon to mujhe barray din ke azaab ka khauf hai
  6,16,jis shakhs se is roz azaab taall diya gaya is par khuda ne ( barri ) meharbani farmai aur yeh khuli kamyabi hai
  6,17,aur agar khuda tum ko koi sakhti pohnchaye to is ke siwa is ko koi daur karne wala nahi aur agar Nemat ( o rahat ) ataa kere to ( koi is ko roknay wala nahi ) woh har cheez par Qadir hai
  6,18,aur woh apne bundon par ghalib hai aur woh Dana aur khabardaar hai
  6,19,un se pucho ke sab se barh kar ( qareen insaaf ) kis ki shahadat hai keh do ke khuda hi mujh mein aur tum mein gawah hai aur yeh quran mujh par is liye utaara gaya hai ke is ke zariye se tum ko aur jis shakhs taq woh poanch sakay aagah kardoonkiya tum log is baat ki shahadat dete ho ke khuda ke sath aur bhi mabood hain ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam! ) keh do ke mein to ( aisi ) shahadat nahi deta keh do ke sirf wohi aik mabood hai aur jin ko tum log shareek banatay ho mein un se bezaar hon
  6,20,jin logon ko hum ne kitaab di hai woh un ( hamaray peghamber ) ko is terhan pehchante hain jis terhan apne beton ko pehchana karte hain jinhon ne apne tain nuqsaan mein daal rakha hai woh imaan nahi laatay
  6,21,aur is shakhs se ziyada kon zalim hai jis ne khuda par jhoot iftirakiya ya is ki ayaton ko jhatlaya. kuch shak nahi ke zalim log nijaat nahi payen ge
  6,22,aur jis din hum sab logon ko jama karen ge phir mushrikon se poucheen ge ke ( aaj ) woh tumahray shareek kahan hain jin ko tumhe daawa tha
  6,23,to un se kuch izr nah ban parre ga ( aur ) bajuz is ke ( kuch charah nah hoga ) ke kahin khuda ki qasam jo hamara perwar-digaar hai hum shareek nahi banatay they
  6,24,dekho unhon ne apne oopar kaisa jhoot bola aur jo kuch yeh iftirakiya karte they sab un se jata raha
  6,25,aur un mein baaz aisay hain ke tumhari ( baton ki ) taraf kaan rakhtay hain. aur hum ne un ke dilon par to parday daal diye hain ke un ko samajh nah saken aur kaanon mein saqal peda kardiya hai ( ke sun nah saken ) aur agar yeh tamam nishanain bhi dekh len tab bhi un par imaan nah layein. yahan taq ke jab tumahray paas tum se behas karne ko atay hain to jo kafir hain kehte hain yeh ( quran ) aur kuch bhi nahi sirf pehlay logon ki kahaniyan hain
  6,26,woh is se ( ouron ko bhi ) roktay hain aur khud bhi paray rehtay hain magar ( un baton se ) apne aap hi ko halaak karte hain aur ( is se ) be khabar hain
  6,27,kash tum ( un ko is waqt ) dekho jab yeh dozakh ke kinare kharray kiye jayen ge aur kahin ge ke ae kash hum phir ( duniya mein ) lota diye jayen taakay apne perwar-digaar ki ayaton ki takzieeb nah karen aur momin ho jaien
  6,28,haan yeh jo kuch pehlay chupaya karte they ( aaj ) un par zahir hogaya hai aur agar yeh ( duniya mein ) lout’tay bhi jayen to jin ( kamon ) se un ko manakiya gaya tha wohi phir karne lagen. kuch shak nahi ke yeh jhutay hain
  6,29,aur kehte hain ke hamari jo duniya ki zindagi hai bas yahi ( zindagi ) hai aur hum ( marnay ke baad ) phir zindah nahi kiye jayen ge
  6,30,aur kash tum ( un ko is waqt ) dekho jab yeh apne perwar-digaar ke samnay kharray kiye jayen ge aur woh farmaiye gakiya yeh ( dobarah zindah hona ) barhaq nahi to kahin ge kyun nahi perwar-digaar ki qasam ( bilkul barhaq hai ) khuda farmaiye ga ab kufar ke badlay ( jo duniya mein karte they ) azaab ( ke mazay ) chako
  6,31,jin logon ne khuda ke rubaroo haazir honay ko jhoot samgha woh ghatay mein aagaye. yahan taq ke jab un par qayamat nagahan آموجود hogi to bol utheen ge ke ( haae ) is taqseer par afsos hai jo hum ne qayamat ke baray mein ki. aur woh apne ( aamaal ke ) boojh apni pithon par uthaye hue hon ge. dekho jo boojh yeh utha rahay hain bohat bura hai
  6,32,aur duniya ki zindagi to aik khail aur mashgolah hai. aur bohat acha ghar to akhirat ka ghar hai ( yani ) un ke liye jo ( khuda se ) drtay hain.kiya tum samajte nahi
  6,33,hum ko maloom hai ke un ( kafiroon ) ki baatein tumhe ranj pohanchati hain ( magar ) yeh tumhari takzieeb nahi karte balkay zalim khuda ki ayaton se inkaar karte hain
  6,34,aur tum se pehlay kabhi paighambar jhutlaye jatay rahay to woh takzieeb aur aeza par sabr karte rahay yahan taq ke un ke paas hamari madad pahunchti rahi aur khuda ki baton ko koi bhi badalny wala nahi. aur tum ko payghambaroon ( ke ahwaal ) ki khabrain poanch chuki hain ( to tum bhi sabr se kaam lau )
  6,35,aur agar un ki rogrdani tum par shaq guzarti hai to agar taaqat ho to zameen mein koi surang dhoond nikalu ya aasman mein seerhi ( talaash karo ) phir un ke paas koi moujza lao. aur agar khuda chahta to sab ko hadaayat par jama kardaita pas tum hargiz نادانوں mein nah hona
  6,36,baat yeh hai ke ( haq ko ) qubool wohi karte hain jo suntay bhi hain aur mardon ko to khuda ( qayamat hi ko ) uthaye ga. phir isi ki taraf lout kar jayen ge
  6,37,aur kehte hain ke un par un ke parwar -digaar ke paas koi nishani kyun nazil nahi hui. keh do ke khuda nishani utaarnay par Qadir hai lekin aksar log nahi jantay
  6,38,aur zameen mein jo chalne phirnay wala ( hewan ) ya do paron se urrnay wala janwar hai un ki bhi tum logon ki terhan jamaten hain. hum ne kitaab ( yani looh mehfooz ) mein kisi cheez ( ke likhnay ) mein kotahi nahi ki phir sab apne perwar-digaar ki taraf jama kiye jayen ge
  6,39,aur jin logon ne hamari ayaton ko jhatlaya woh behray aur gungay hain ( is ke ilawa ) andheray mein ( parre hue ) jis ko khuda chahay gumraah kardey aur jisay chahay seedhay raste par chala day
  6,40,kaho ( kafroo ) bhala dekho to agar tum par khuda ka azaab aajay ya qayamat آموجود ho tokiya tum ( aisi haalat mein ) khuda ke siwa kisi aur ko poukaro ge? agar sachey ho ( to batao )
  6,41,balkay ( museebat ke waqt tum ) isi ko pkarte ho to jis dukh ke liye usay pkarte ho. woh agar chahta hai to is ko daur kardaita hai aur jin ko tum shareek banatay ho ( is waqt ) inhen bhool jatay ho
  6,42,aur hum ne tum se pehlay bohat si amton ki taraf paighambar beje. phir ( un ki nafarmaniyon ke sabab ) hum inhen sakhtiyon aur tklifon mein pakarte rahay taakay aajzi karen
  6,43,to jab un par hamara azaab aata raha kyun nahi aajzi karte rahay. magar un ke to dil hi sakht hogaye they. aur jo woh kaam karte they shetan un ko ( un ki nazron mein ) aaraasta kar dekhata tha
  6,44,phir jab unhon ne is nasiyaat ko jo un ko ke gayi thi faramosh kardiya to hum ne un par har cheez ke darwazay khol diye. yahan taq ke jab un cheezon se jo un ko di gayi theen khoob khush hogaye to hum ne un ko nagahan pakar liya aur woh is waqt mayoos ho kar reh gay
  6,45,gharz zalim logon ki jarr kaat di gayi. aur sab tareef khuday-e rab alameen hi ko ( sazawar hai )
  6,46,( un kafiroon se ) kaho ke bhala dekho to agar khuda tumahray kaan aur ankhen chean le aur tumahray dilon par mohar lagade to خداکے siwa kon sa mabood hai jo tumhe yeh naematain phir bakhshay? dekho hum kis kis terhan apni ayatain bayan karte hain. phir bhi yeh log ro gardani karte hain
  6,47,kaho ke bhala batao to agar tum par khuda ka azaab be khaberi mein ya khabar anay ke baad aeye tokiya zalim logon ke siwa koi aur bhi halaak hoga ?
  6,48,aur hum jo payghambaroon ko bhaijtay rahay hain to khushkhabri sunanay aur darane ko phir jo shakhs imaan laaye aur nekokaar hojaye to aisay logon ko nah kuch khauf hoga aur nah woh andohnak hon ge
  6,49,aur jinhon ne hamari ayaton ko jhatlaya un ki nafarmaniyon ke sabab inhen azaab hoga
  6,50,keh do ke mein tum se yeh nahi kehta ke mere paas allah taala ke khazanay hain aur nah ( yeh ke ) mein ghaib jaanta hon aur nah tum se yeh kehta ke mein farishta hon. mein to sirf is hukum par chalta hon jo mujhe ( khuda ki taraf se ) aata hai. keh do ke bhala andha aur aankhh walay barabar hotay hain? to phir tum ghhor kyun nahi karte
  6,51,"aur jo log jo khauf rakhtay hain ke apne perwar-digaar ke rubaroo haazir kiye jayen ge ( aur jantay hain ke ) is ke siwa nah to un ka koi dost hoga aur nah sifarish karne wala, un ko is ( quran ) ke zariye se nasiyaat kar do taakay parhaizgaar banin"
  6,52,aur jo log subah vsham apni perwar-digaar se dua karte hain ( aur ) is ki zaat ke taalib hain un ko ( apne paas se ) mat nikalu. un ke hisaab ( aamaal ) ki jawab dahi tum par kuch nahi aur tumahray hisaab ki jawab dahi un par kuch nahi ( pas aisa nah karna ) agar un konikalo ge to zaalmon mein ho jao ge
  6,53,aur isi terhan hum ne baaz logon ki baaz se azmaish ki hai ke ( jo doltmnd hain woh ghareebon ki nisbat ) kehte hainkiya yahi log hain jin par khuda ne hum mein se fazlkiya hai ( khuda ne farmaya ) bhala khuda shukar karne walon se waaqif nahi ?
  6,54,aur jab tumahray paas aisay log aaya karen jo hamari ayaton par imaan laatay hain to ( un se ) salam alaikum kaha karo khuda ne apni zaat ( pak ) par rehmat ko lazim karliya hai ke jo koi tum mein nadani se koi buri harkat kar baithy phir is ke baad tauba karle aur nekokaar hojaye to woh bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  6,55,aur is terhan hum apni ayatain khol khol kar bayan karte hain ( taakay tum log un par amal karo ) aur is liye ke gunahgaaron ka rasta zahir hojaye
  6,56,( ae paighambar! kufar se ) keh do ke jin ko tum khuda ke siwa pkarte ho mujhe un ki ibadat se manakiya gaya hai. ( yeh bhi ) keh do ke mein tumhari khawahishon ki pairwi nahi karoon ga aisa karoon to gumraah hojaon aur hadaayat Yafta logon mein nah rahon
  6,57,keh do ke mein to apne perwar-digaar ki Daleel roshan par hon aur tum is ki takzieeb karte ho. jis cheez ( yani azaab ) ke liye tum jaldi kar rahay ho woh mere paas nahi hai ( aisa ) hukum allah hi ke ikhtiyar mein hai woh sachhi baat bayan farmata hai aur woh sab se behtar faisla karne wala hai
  6,58,keh do ke jis cheez ke liye tum jaldi kar rahay ho agar woh mere ikhtiyar mein hoti to mujh mein aur tum mein faisla hochuka hota. aur khuda zaalmon se khoob waaqif hai
  6,59,aur isi ke paas ghaib ki knjyan hain jin ko is ke siwa koi nahi jaanta. aur usay junglon aur daryaaon ki sab cheezon ka ilm hai. aur koi pata nahi jharta magar woh is ko jaanta hai aur zameen ke andheron mein koi dana aur koi hari aur sookhi cheez nahi hai magar kitaab roshan mein ( likhi hui ) hai
  6,60,aur wohi to hai jo raat ko ( sonay ki haalat mein ) tumhari rooh qabz karleta hai aur jo kuch tum din mein karte ho is se khabar rakhta hai phir tumhe din ko utha deta hai taakay ( yahi silsila jari rakh kar zindagi ki ) Moueen muddat poori kar di jaye phir tum ( sab ) ko isi ki taraf lout kar jana hai ( is roz ) woh tum ko tumahray amal jo tum karte ho ( aik aik karkay ) betaye ga
  6,61,aur woh apne bundon par ghalib hai. aur tum par nigehbaan muqarrar kiye rakhta hai. yahan taq ke jab tum mein se kisi ki mout aati hai to hamaray farishtay is ki rooh qabz kar lete hain aur woh kisi terhan ki kotahi nahi karte
  6,62,phir ( qayamat ke din tamam ) log apne maalik barhaq khuda taala ke paas wapas bulaye jayen ge. sun lau ke hukum isi ka hai aur woh nihayat jald hisaab lainay wala hai
  6,63,kaho bhala tum ko junglon aur daryaaon ke andheron se kon mukhlasi deta hai ( jab ) ke tum usay aajzi aur niaz pinhani se pkarte ho ( aur kehte ho ) agar khuda hum ko is ( tangi ) se nijaat bakhshay to hum is ke bohat shukar guzaar hon
  6,64,kaho ke khuda hi tum ko is ( tangi ) se aur har sakhti se nijaat bakhshta hai. phir ( tum ) is ke sath shirk karte ho
  6,65,keh do ke woh ( is par bhi ) qudrat rakhta hai ke tum par oopar ki taraf se ya tumahray paon ke neechay se azaab beje ya tumhe firqa firqa kardey aur aik ko dosray ( se lara kar aapas ) ki larai ka maza chakha de. dekho hum apni ayaton ko kis kis terhan bayan karte hain taakay yeh log samjhain
  6,66,aur is ( quran ) ko tumhari qoum ne jhatlaya halaank woh sara sar haq hai. keh do ke mein tumhara Darogha nahi hon
  6,67,har khabar ke liye aik waqt muqarrar hai aur tum ko anqareeb maloom hojaye ga
  6,68,aur jab tum aisay logon ko dekho jo hamari ayaton ke baray mein behooda bakwaas kar rahay hon to un se allag hojao yahan taq ke aur baton mein masroof ho jaien. aur agar ( yeh baat ) shetan tumhe bhala day to yaad anay par zalim logon ke sath nah betho
  6,69,aur parhaiz garon par un logon ke hisaab ki kuch bhi jawab dahi nahi haan nasiyaat taakay woh bhi parhaizgaar hon
  6,70,aur jin logon ne apne deen ko khail aur tamasha bana rakha hai aur duniya ki zindagi ne un ko dhokay mein daal rakha hai un se kuch kaam nah rakho haan is ( quran ) ke zariye se nasiyaat karte raho taakay ( qayamat ke din ) koi apne aamaal ki saza mein halakat mein nah dala jaye ( is roz ) khuda ke siwa nah to koi is ka dost hoga aur nah sifarish karne wala. aur agar woh har cheez ( jo roye zameen par hai bator ) muawza dena chahay to woh is se qubool nah ho yahi log hain ke apne aamaal ke wabaal mein halakat mein daaley gay un ke liye peenay ko kholta howa pani aur dukh dainay wala azaab hai is liye ke kufar karte they
  6,71,kaho.kiya hum khuda ke siwa aisi cheez ko pukaarain jo nah hamara bhala kar sakay nah bura. aur jab hum ko khuda ne seedha rasta dikha diya to (kiya ) hum ultay paon phir jayen? ( phir hamari aisi misaal ho ) jaisay kisi ko jaanat ne jungle mein bhala diya ho ( aur woh ) heran ( ho raha ho ) aur is ke kuch Rafeeq hon jo is ko raste ki taraf bulayen ke hamaray paas chala aa. keh do ke rasta to wohi hai jo khuda ne bataya hai. aur hamein to yeh hukum mila hai ke hum khuday-e rab alameen ke farmanbardar hon
  6,72,aur yeh ( bhi ) ke namaz parhte raho aur is se drtay raho. aur wohi to hai jis ke paas tum jama kiye jao ge
  6,73,aur wohi to hai jis ne asmano aur zameen ko tadbeer se pedakiya hai. aur jis din woh farmaiye ga ke ho ja to ( hashar barpaa ) hojaye ga. is ka irshad barhaq hai. aur jis din sor phonka jaye ga ( is din ) isi ki badshahat hogi. wohi posheeda aur zahir ( sab ) ka jan-nay wala hai aur wohi Dana aur khabardaar hai
  6,74,aur ( woh waqt bhi yaad karne ke Laiq hai ) jab ibrahim ne apne baap Azar se kaha ke tum buton kokiya mabood banatay ho. mein daikhta hon ke tum aur tumhari qoum Sarih gumraahi mein ho
  6,75,aur hum is terhan ibrahim ko asmano aur zameen ke ajaebaat dikhaane lagey taakay woh khoob yaqeen karne walon mein ho jaien
  6,76,( yani ) jab raat ne un ko ( پردہٴ tareqi se ) dhaanp liya ( to aasman mein ) aik sitaara nazar para. kehnay lagey yeh mera perwar-digaar hai. jab woh gayab hogaya to kehnay lagey ke mujhe gayab hojane walay pasand nahi
  6,77,phir jab chaand ko dekha ke chamak raha hai to kehnay lagey yeh mera perwar-digaar hai. lekin jab woh bhi choup gaya to bol utthay ke mera perwar-digaar mujhe seedha rasta nahi dukhaay ga to mein un logon mein hojaon ga jo bhatak rahay hain
  6,78,phir jab Sooraj ko dekha ke jagmaga raha hai to kehnay lagey mera perwar-digaar yeh hai yeh sab se bara hai. magar jab woh bhi ghuroob hogaya to kehnay lagey logo! jin cheezon ko tum ( khuda ka ) shareek banatay ho mein un se bezaar hon
  6,79,mein ne sab se yaksu ho kar apne tain isi zaat ki taraf mutwajjahkiya jis ne asmano aur zameen ko pedakiya hai aur mein mushrikon mein se nahi hon
  6,80,aur un ki qoum un se behas karne lagi to unhon ne kaha ke tum mujh se khuda ke baray mein (kiya ) behas karte ho is ne to mujhe seedha rasta dikha diya hai. aur jin cheezon ko tum is ka shareek banatay ho mein un se nahi darta. haan jo mera perwar-digaar chahay. mera perwar-digaar apne ilm se har cheez par ihata kiye hue hai.kiya tum khayaal nahi karte .
  6,81,bhala mein un cheezon se jin ko tum ( khuda ka ) shareek banatay ho kunkar Daron jab ke tum is se nahi drtay ke khuda ke sath shareek banatay ho jis ki is ne koi sanad nazil nahi ki. ab dono fareeq mein se kon sa fareeq aman ( aur jamiat khatir ) ka mustahiq hai. agar samajh rakhtay ho ( to batao )
  6,82,jo log imaan laaye aur apne imaan ko ( shirk ke ) zulm se makhloot nahikiya un ke aman ( aur jamiat khatir ) hai aur wohi hadaayat panay walay hain
  6,83,aur yeh hamari Daleel thi jo hum ne ibrahim ko un ki qoum ke muqablay mein ataa ki thi. hum jis ke chahtay hain darjay buland kardete hain. be shak tumhara perwar-digaar Dana aur khabardaar hai
  6,84,aur hum ne un ko Ishaq aur Yaqoob bakhshay. ( aur ) sab ko hadaayat di. aur pehlay Nooh ko bhi hadaayat di thi aur un ki aulaad mein se dawod aur Sulaiman aur ayub aur Yousuf aur moose aur Haroon ko bhi. aur hum naik logon ko aisa hi badla diya karte hain
  6,85,aur zikria aur yahya aur eesa aur Ilyas ko bhi. yeh sab nekokaar they
  6,86,aur asmayl aur اallyaasa aur Younis aur Loot ko bhi. aur un sab ko Jahan ke logon par fazliat bakhsh thi
  6,87,aur baaz baaz ko un ke baap dada aur aulaad aur bhaiyon mein se bhi. aur un ko bargzida bhikiya tha aur seedha rasta bhi dekhaya tha
  6,88,yeh khuda ki hadaayat hai is par apne bundon mein se jisay chahay chalaye. aur agar woh log shirk karte to jo amal woh karte they sab zaya ho jatay
  6,89,yeh woh log they jin ko hum ne kitaab aur hukum ( Shariat ) aur nabuwat ataa farmai thi. agar yeh ( kufar ) un baton se inkaar karen to hum ne un par ( imaan laane ke liye ) aisay log muqarrar kardiye hain ke woh un se kabhi inkaar karne walay nahi
  6,90,yeh woh log hain jin ko khuda ne hadaayat di thi to tum inhen ki hadaayat ki pairwi karo. keh do ke mein tum se is ( quran ) ka sila nahi mangta. yeh to Jahan ke logon ke liye mehez nasiyaat hai
  6,91,aur un logon ne khuda ki qader jaisi jaan-ni chahiye thi nah jani. jab unhon ne kaha ke khuda ne ensaan par ( wahi aur kitaab waghera ) kuch bhi nazil nahikiya. kaho jo kitaab moose le kar aeye they usay kis ne nazilkiya tha jo logon ke liye noor aur hadaayat thi aur jisay tum ne alehda alehda ourak ( par naqal ) kar rakha hai un ( ke kuch hissay ) ko to zahir karte ho aur aksar ko chupatay ho. aur tum ko woh baatein sikhayi gayeen jin ko nah tum jantay they aur nah tumahray baap dada. keh do ( is kitaab ko ) khuda hi ne ( nazilkiya tha ) phir un ko chore diya ke apni behooda bakwaas mein khailtay rahen
  6,92,aur ( waisi hi ) yeh kitaab hai jisay hum ne nazilkiya hai babarkat jo apne se pehli ( kitabon ) ki tasdeeq karti hai aur ( jo ) is liye ( nazil ki gayi hai ) ke tum mukkay aur is ke aas paas ke logon ko aagah kardo. aur jo log akhirat par imaan rakhtay hain woh is kitaab par bhi imaan rakhtay hain aur woh apni namazon ki poori khabar rakhtay hain
  6,93,aur is se barh kar zalim kon hoga jo khuda par jhoot iftira kere. ya yeh kahe ke mujh par wahi aayi hai halaank is par kuch bhi wahi nah aayi ho aur jo yeh kahe ke jis terhan ki kitaab khuda ne nazil ki hai is terhan ki mein bhi bana laita hon. aur kash tum un zalim ( yani mushriq ) logon ko is waqt dekho jab mout ki sakhtiyon mein ( mubtala ) hon aur farishtay ( un ki taraf azaab ke liye ) haath barha rahay hon ke nikalu apni jaanen. aaj tum ko zillat ke azaab ki saza di jaye gi is liye ke tum khuda par jhoot bola karte they aur is ki ayaton se sar kashi karte they
  6,94,aur jaissa hum ne tum ko pehli dafaa pedakiya tha aisa hi aaj akailey akailey hamaray paas aeye aur jo ( maal o mata'a) hum ne tumhe ataa farmaya tha woh sab apni peeth peechay chore aeye aur hum tumahray sath tumahray sifarshion ko bhi nahi dekhte jin ki nisbat tum khayaal karte they ke woh tumahray ( Shafi aur hamaray ) shareek hain. ( aaj ) tumahray aapas ke sab taluqaat munhqita hogaye aur jo daaway tumkiya karte they sab jatay rahay
  6,95,be shak khuda hi danay aur ghuthli ko phaar kar ( un se darakht waghera )ugaataا hai wohi jandaar ko be jaan se nikalta hai aur wohi be jaan ka jandaar se nikaalte wala hai. yahi to khuda hai. phir tum kahan behke phirtay ho
  6,96,wohi ( raat ke andheray se ) subah ki roshni phaar nikalta hai aur isi ne raat ko ( mojab ) aaraam ( thehraya ) aur Sooraj aur chaand ko ( zaraye ) shumaar banaya hai. yeh khuda ke ( muqarrar kiye hue ) andazay hain jo ghalib ( aur ) ilm wala hai
  6,97,aur wohi to hai jis ne tumahray liye setaaray banaye taakay junglon aur daryaaon ke andheron mein un se raste maloom karo. aqal walon ke liye hum ne apni ayatain khol khol kar bayan kar di hain
  6,98,aur wohi to hai jis ne tum ko 1 shakhs se pedakiya. phir ( tumahray liye ) aik theharnay ki jagah hai aur aik supurd honay ki samajhney walon ke liye hum ne ( apni ) ayatain khol khol kar bayan kar di hain
  6,99,aur wohi to hai jo aasman semeinh barsata hai. phir hum hi ( jomeinh barastee hain ) is se har terhan ki roedgi ogatay hain. phir is mein se sabz sabz konplen nikaltay hain. aur un konpalon mein se aik dosray ke sath jurey hue danay nikaltay hain aur khajoor ke gabeh mein se lataktay hue guchay aur angarro ke baagh aur Zaitoon aur aanar jo aik dosray se mlitay jaltay bhi hain. aur nahi bhi mlitay. yeh cheezein jab phalti hain to un ke phalon par aur ( jab pkti hain to ) un ke paknay par nazar karo. un mein un logon ke liye jo imaan laatay hain ( qudrat khuda ki bohat si ) nishanain hain
  6,100,aur un logon ne junoo ko khuda ka shareek thehraya. halaank un ko isi ne pedakiya aur be samjhay ( jhoot bohtan ) is ke liye betay aur betiyan bana khari kee woh un baton se jo is ki nisbat bayan karte hain pak hai aur ( is ki shaan un se ) buland hai
  6,101,( wohi ) asmano aur zameen ka peda karne wala ( hai ). is ke aulaad kahan se ho jab ke is ki biwi hi nahi. aur is ne har cheez ko pedakiya hai. aur woh har cheez se bakhabar hai
  6,102,yahi ( Awsaf rakhnay wala ) khuda tumhara perwar-digaar hai. is ke siwa koi mabood nahi. ( wohi ) har cheez ka paida karnay wala ( hai ) to isi ki ibadat karo. aur woh har cheez ka nigaran hai
  6,103,( woh aisa hai ke ) nigehain is ka idraak nahi krsktin aur woh nigahon ka idraak karsaktha hai aur woh bhaid jan-nay wala khabardaar hai
  6,104,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam! un se keh do ke ) tumahray ( paas ) perwar-digaar ki taraf se ( roshan ) daleelen poanch chuki hain to jis ne ( un ko aankhh khol kar ) dekha is ne apna bhalakiya aur jo andha bana raha is ne apne haq mein burakiya. aur mein tumhara nigehbaan nahi hon
  6,105,aur hum isi terhan apni ayatain phair phair kar bayan karte hain taakay kafir yeh nah kahin ke tum ( yeh baatein ahal kitaab se ) sekhe hue ho aur taakay samajhney walay logon ke liye tashreeh kar dein
  6,106,aur jo hukum tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se tumahray paas aata hai isi ki pairwi karo. is ( perwar-digaar ) ke siwa koi mabood nahi. aur mushrikon se kinara karlo
  6,107,aur agar khuda chahta to yeh log shirk nah karte. aur ( ae paighambar! ) hum ne tum ko un par nigehbaan muqarrar nahikiya. aur nah tum un ke Darogha ho
  6,108,aur jin logon ko yeh mushriq khuda ke siwa pkarte hain un ko bura nah kehna ke yeh bhi kahin khuda ko be adbi se be samjhay bura ( nah ) keh bathain. is terhan hum ne har aik firqay ke aamaal ( un ki nazron mein ) achay kar dukhaay hain. phir un ko apne perwar-digaar kaaf taraf lout kar jana hai tab woh un ko betaye ga ke wohkiyakiya karte they
  6,109,aur yeh log khuda ki sakht sakht kasmain khatay hain ke agar un ke paas koi nishani aeye to woh is par zurori imaan le ayen. keh do ke nishanain to sab khuda hi ke paas hain. aur ( momino! ) tumhekiya maloom hai ( yeh to aisay badbakht hain ke un ke paas ) nishanain aa bhi jayen tab bhi imaan nah layein
  6,110,aur hum un ke dilon aur aankhon ko ulat den ge ( to ) jaisay yeh is ( quran ) par pehli dafaa imaan nahi laaye ( waisay phir nah layein ge ) aur un ko chore den ge ke apni sar kashi mein behektey rahen
  6,111,aur agar hum un par farishtay bhi utaar dete aur murdy bhi un se guftagu karne lagtay aur hum sab cheezon ko un ke samnay laa mojood bhi kar dete to bhi yeh imaan laane walay nah they ila mashah allah baat yeh hai ke yeh aksar nadaan hain
  6,112,aur isi terhan hum ne shetan ( seerat ) insanon aur junoo ko har paighambar ka dushman bana diya tha woh dhoka dainay ke liye aik dosray ke dil mein mulamma ki baatein daaltay rehtay they aur agar tumhara perwar-digaar chahta to woh aisa nah karte to un ko aur jo kuch yeh iftira karte hain usay chore do
  6,113,aur ( woh aisay kaam ) is liye bhi ( karte they ) ke jo log akhirat par imaan nahi rakhtay un ke dil un ki baton par mael hon aur woh inhen pasand karen aur jo kaam woh karte they woh hi karne lagen
  6,114,( kaho )kiya mein khuda ke siwa aur munhsif talaash karoon halaank is ne tumhari taraf wazay ul matalib kitaab bhaije hai aur jin logon ko hum ne kitaab ( torat ) di hai woh jantay hain ke woh tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se barhaq nazil hui hai to tum hargiz shak karne walon mein nah hona
  6,115,aur tumahray perwar-digaar ki baatein sachaai aur insaaf mein poori hain is ki baton ko koi badalny wala nahi aur woh santa jaanta hai
  6,116,aur aksar log jo zameen par abad hain ( gumraah hain ) agar tum un ka kaha maan lau ge to woh tumhe khuda ka rasta bhala den ge yeh mehez khayaal ke peechay chaltay aur niray atkal ke teer chillate hain
  6,117,tumhara perwar-digaar un logon ko khoob jaanta hai jo is ke raste se bhatkay hue hain aur un se bhi khoob waaqif hai jo raste par chal rahay hain
  6,118,to jis cheez par ( zibah ke waqt ) khuda ka naam liya jaye agar tum is ki ayaton par imaan rakhtay ho to usay kha liya karo
  6,119,aur sababkiya hai ke jis cheez par khuda ka naam liya jaye tum usay nah khao halaank jo cheezein is ne tumahray liye haraam ٹھیرا di hain woh aik aik kar ke bayan kar di hain ( be shak un ko nahi khana chahiye ) magar is soorat mein ke un ke ( khanay ke ) liye nachar ho jao aur bohat se log be samjhay boojhay apne nafs ki khawahishon se logon ko b_hka rahay hain kuch shak nahi ke aisay logon ko jo ( khuda ki muqarrar ki hui ) hadd se bahar nikal jatay hain tumhara perwar-digaar khoob jaanta hai
  6,120,aur zahiri aur posheeda ( har terhan ka ) gunah tark kar do jo log gunah karte hain woh anqareeb apne kiye ki saza payen ge
  6,121,aur jis cheez par khuda ka naam nah liya jaye usay mat khao ke is ka khana gunah hai aur shetan ( log ) apne rfiqon ke dilon mein yeh baat daaltay hain ke tum se jhagra karen aur agar tum log un ke kahe par chalay to be shak tum bhi mushriq hue
  6,122,bhala jo pehlay murda tha phir hum ne is ko zindahkiya aur is ke liye roshni kar di jis ke zariye se woh logon mein chalta phirta hai kahin is shakhs jaissa ho sakta hai jo andheray mein para howa ho aur is se nikal hi nah sakay isi terhan kafir jo amal kar rahay hain woh inhen achay maloom hotay hain
  6,123,aur isi terhan hum ne har bastii mein barray barray mujrim peda kiye ke un meinmakaryan karte rahen aur jomakaryan yeh karte hain un ka nuqsaan inhen ko hai aur ( is se ) be khabar hain
  6,124,aur jab un ke paas koi aayat aati hai to kehte hain ke jis terhan ki risalat khuda ke payghambaroon ko mili hai jab taq isi terhan ki risalat hum ko nah miley hum hargiz imaan nahi layein ge is ko khuda hi khoob jaanta hai ke ( risalat ka kon sa mehal hai aur ) woh apni paigambri kisay inayat farmaiye jo log jurm karte hain un ko khuda ke haan zillat aur azabِ shadeed hoga is liye kemakaryan karte they
  6,125,to jis shakhs ko khuda chahta hai ke hadaayat bakhshay is ka seenah islam ke liye khol deta hai aur jisay chahta hai ke gumraah kere is ka seenah tang aur ghata howa kar deta hai goya woh aasman par charh raha hai is terhan khuda un logon par jo imaan nahi laatay azaab bhejta hai
  6,126,aur yahi tumahray perwar-digaar ka seedha rasta hai jo log ghhor karne walay hain un ke liye hum ne apni ayatain khol khol kar bayan kar di hain
  6,127,un ke liye un ke aamaal ke siilay mein perwar-digaar ke haan salamti ka ghar hai aur wohi un ka Dostdar hai
  6,128,aur jis din woh sab ( jin o ins ) ko jama kere ga ( aur farmaiye ga ke ) ae giroh jinnaat tum ne insanon se bohat ( faiday ) haasil kiye to jo insanon mein un ke Dostdar hon ge woh kahin ge ke perwar-digaar hum aik dosray se faida uthatay rahay aur ( aakhir ) is waqt ko poanch gay jo to ne hamaray liye muqarrarkiya tha khuda farmaiye ga ( ab ) tumhara thikana dozakh hai hamesha is mein ( jaltay ) raho ge magar jo khuda chahay be shak tumhara perwar-digaar Dana aur khabardaar hai
  6,129,aur isi terhan hum zaalmon ko un ke aamaal ke sabab jo woh karte they aik dosray par musallat kar dete hain
  6,130,ae junoo aur insanon ki jamaatkiya tumahray paas tum hi mein se paighambar nahi atay rahay jo meri ayatain tum ko parh parh kar sunaate aur is din ke samnay آموجود honay se darate they woh kahin ge ke ( perwar-digaar ) hamein apne gunaaho ka iqraar hai un logon ko dnyaki zindagi ne dhokay mein daal rakha tha aur ( ab ) khud apne oopar gawahi di ke kufar karte they
  6,131,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam! ) yeh ( jo paighambar atay rahay aur kitaaben nazil hoti rahen to ) is liye ke tumhara perwar-digaar aisa nahi ke bustiyon ko zulm se halaak kar day aur wahan ke rehne walon ko ( kuch bhi ) khabar nah ho
  6,132,aur sab logon ke bilhaaz aamaal darjay ( muqarrar ) hain aur jo kaam yeh log karte hain khuda un se be khabar nahi
  6,133,aur tumhara perwar-digaar be parwa ( aur ) sahib rehmat hai agar chahay ( to ae bundon ) tumhe nabood kar day aur tumahray baad jin logon ko chahay tumhara janasheen bana day jaissa tum ko bhi dosray logon ki nasal se pedakiya hai
  6,134,kuch shak nahi ke jo wada tum sekiya jata hai woh ( wuqoo mein ) anay wala hai aur tum ( khuda ko ) maghloob nahi kar satke
  6,135,keh do ke logo tum apni jagah amal kiye jao mein ( apni jagah ) amal kiye jata hon anqareeb tum ko maloom ho jaye ga ke akhirat mein ( bahisht ) kis ka ghar hoga kuch shak nahi ke mushriq nijaat nahi panay ke
  6,136,aur ( yeh log ) khuda hi ki peda ki hui cheezon yani khaiti aur chopaiyon mein khuda ka bhi aik hissa muqarrar karte hain aur apne khayaal ( baatil ) se kehte hain ke yeh ( hissa ) to khuda ka aur yeh hamaray sharikon ( yani buton ) ka to jo hissa un ke sharikon ka hota hai woh to khuda ki taraf nahi ja sakta aur jo hissa khuda ka hota hai woh un ke sharikon ki taraf ja sakta hai yeh kaisa bura insaaf hai
  6,137,isi terhan bohat se mushrikon ko un ke sharikon ne un ke bachon ko jaan se maar daalna acha kar dekhaya hai taakay inhen halakat mein daal den aur un ke deen ko un par khalt malt kar den aur agar khuda chahta to woh aisa nah karte to un ko chore do ke woh jaanen aur un ka jhoot
  6,138,aur apne khayaal se yeh bhi kehte hain ke yeh charpaye aur khaiti mana hai usay is shakhs ke siwa jisay hum chahain koi nah khaye aur ( baaz ) charpaye aisay hain ke un ki pait par charhna mana kar diya gaya hai aur baaz maweshi aisay hain jin par ( zibah karte waqt ) khuda ka naam nahi letay sab khuda par jhoot hai woh anqareeb un ko un ke jhoot ka badla day ga
  6,139,aur yeh bhi kehte hain ke jo bacha un charpayon ke pait mein hai woh khaas hamaray mardon ke liye hai aur hamari aurton ko ( is ka khana ) haraam hai aur agar woh bacha mra howa ho to sab is mein shareek hain ( yani usay mard aur aurtain sab khayen ) anqareeb khuda un ko un ke dhkoslon ki saza day ga be shak woh hikmat wala khabardaar hai
  6,140,jin logon ne apni aulaad ko bewakofi se be samjhi se qatalkiya aur khuda par aftara kar ke is ki ataa farmai ki hui rozi ko haraam t_hraya woh ghatay mein par gay woh be shuba gumraah hain aur hadaayat Yafta nahi hain
  6,141,aur khuda hi to hai jis ne baagh peda kiye chatriyon par charhaye hue bhi aur jo chatriyon par nahi charhaye hue woh bhi aur khajoor aur khaiti jin ke terhan terhan ke phal hotay hain aur Zaitoon aur aanar jo ( baaz baton mein ) aik dosray se mlitay hain jab yeh cheezein phalain to un ke phal khao aur jis din ( phal torro aur khaiti ) katu to khuda ka haq bhi is mein se ada karo aur be ja nah urrao ke khuda beja urane walon ko dost nahi rakhta
  6,142,aur charpayon mein boojh uthany walay ( yani barray barray ) bhi peda kiye aur zameen se lagey hue ( yani chhootey chhootey ) bhi ( pas ) khuda ka diya howa rizaq khao aur shetan ke qadmon par nah chalo woh tumhara Sarih dushman hai
  6,143,( yeh barray chhootey charpaye ) aath qisam ke ( hain ) do ( do ) bheiron mein se aur do ( do ) bakrion mein se ( yani aik aik nar aur aur aik aik madah ) ( ae paighambar un se ) pucho ke ( khuda ne ) dono ( ke ) naron ko haraamkiya hai ya dono ( ki ) madinyon ko ya jo bacha madanyon (madah ) ke pait mein lapat raha ho usay agar sachey ho to mujhe sanad se batao
  6,144,aur do ( do ) avnton mein se aur do ( do ) gayon mein se ( un ke baray mein bhi un se ) pucho ke ( khuda ne ) dono ( ke ) naron ko haraamkiya hai ya dono ( ki ) madanyon ko ya jo bacha madanyon (madah) ke pait mein lapat raha ho is ko bhala jis waqt khuda ne tum ko is ka hukum diya tha tum is waqt mojood they? to is shakhs se ziyada kon zalim hai jo khuda par jhoot iftira kere taakay aِz raah be -danashi logon ko gumraah kere kuch shak nahi ke khuda zalim logon ko hadaayat nahi deta
  6,145,kaho ke jo ehkaam mujh par nazil hue hain un mein koi cheez jisay khanay wala khaye haraam nahi paata bajuz is ke ke woh mra howa janwar ya behta lahoo ya soor ka gosht ke yeh sab napak hain ya koi gunah ki cheez ho ke is par khuda ke siwa kisi aur ka naam liya gaya ho aur agar koi majaboor ho jaye lekin nah to nafarmani kere aur nah hadd se bahar nikal jaye to tumhara perwar-digaar bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  6,146,aur yahudion par hum ne sab naakhun walay janwar haraam kar diye they aur gayon aur bakrion se un ki charbi haraam kar di thi siwa is ke jo un ki peeth par lagi ho ya ojhri mein ho ya haddi mein mili ho yeh saza hum ne un ko un ki shararat ke sabab di thi aur hum to sach kehnay walay hain
  6,147,aur agar yun log tumhari takzieeb karen to keh do tumhara perwar-digaar sahib rehmat wasee hai magar is ka azaab gunah -gaar logon se nahi tallay ga
  6,148,jo log shirk karte hain woh kahin ge ke agar khuda chahta to hum shirk nah karte aur nah hamaray baap dada ( shirk karte ) aur nah hum kisi cheez ko haraam th_hrate isi terhan un logon ne takzieeb ki thi jo un se pehlay they yahan taq ke hamaray azaab ka maza chakh kar rahay keh dokiya tumahray paas koi sanad hai ( agar hai ) to usay hamaray samnay nikalu tum mehez khayaal ke peechay chaltay aur atkal ki teer chillate ho
  6,149,keh do ke khuda hi ki Hujjat ghalib hai agar woh chahta to tum sab ko hadaayat day deta
  6,150,kaho ke apne gawahoon ko lao jo bitayen ke khuda ne yeh cheezein haraam ki hain phir agar woh ( aa kar ) gawahi den to tum un ke sath gawahi nah dena aur nah un logon ki khawahishon ki pairwi karna jo hamari ayaton ko jutlatay hain aur akhirat par imaan nahi laatay aur ( buton ko ) apne perwar-digaar ke barabar th_hrate hain
  6,151,keh ke ( logo ) aao mein tumhe woh cheezein parh kar sunaoon jo tumahray perwar-digaar ne tum par haraam kar di hain ( un ki nisbat is ne is terhan irshad farmaya hai ) ke kisi cheez ko khuda ka shareek nah banana aur maa baap ( se bud sulooki nah karna balkay ) sulooq karte rehna aur nadari ( ke andaishay ) se apni aulaad ko qatal nah karna kyunkay tum ko aur un ko hum hi rizaq dete hain aur be hiyai ke kaam zahir hon ya posheeda un ke paas nah phatakna aur kisi jaan ( walay ) ko jis ke qatal ko khuda ne haraam kar diya hai qatal nah karna magar jaaiz tor par ( yani jis ka Shariat hukum day ) un baton ka woh tumhe irshad farmata hai taakay tum samjhoo
  6,152,aur yateem ke maal ke paas bhi nah jana magar aisay tareeq se ke bohat hi pasandeeda ho yahan taq ke woh jawani ko poanch jaye aur naap toal insaaf ke sath poori poorikiya karo hum kisi ko takleef nahi dete magar is ki taaqat ke mutabiq aur jab ( kisi ki nisbat ) koi baat kaho to insaaf se kaho go woh ( tumhara ) rishta daar hi ho aur khuda ke ehad ko poora karo un baton ka khuda tumhe hukum deta hai taakay tum nasihat karo
  6,153,aur yeh ke mera seedha rasta yahi hai to tum isi par chalna aur aur rustoon par nah chalna ke ( un par chal kar ) khuda ke raste se allag ho jao ge un baton ka khuda tumhe hukum deta hai taakay tum parhaizgaar bano
  6,154,( haan ) phir ( sun lau ke ) hum ne moose ko kitaab inayat ki thi taakay un logon par jo nekokaar hain Nemat poori kar den aur ( is mein ) har cheez ka bayan ( hai ) aur hadaayat ( hai ) aur rehmat hai taakay ( un ki ummat ke ) log apne perwar-digaar ke rubaroo haazir honay ka yaqeen karen
  6,155,aur ( ae kufar karne walon ) yeh kitaab bhi hamein ne utari hai barket wali to is ki pairwi karo aur ( khuda se ) daro taakay tum par meharbani ki jaye
  6,156,( aur is liye utari hai ) ke ( tum yun nah ) kaho ke hum se pehlay do hi garohoon par kitaaben utri theen aur hum un ke parhnay se ( mazoor aur ) be khabar they
  6,157,ya ( yeh nah ) kaho ke agar hum par bhi kitaab nazil hoti to hum un logon ki nisbat kahin seedhay raste par hotay so tumahray paas tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se Daleel aur hadaayat aur rehmat aa gayi hai to is se barh kar zalim kon hoga jo khuda ki ayaton ki takzieeb kere aur un se ( logon ko ) phairay jo log hamari ayaton se phertey hain is phairnay ke sabab hum un ko buray azaab ki saza den ge
  6,158,yeh is ke siwa aur kis baat ke munhtazir hain ke un ke paas farishtay ayen ya khud tumhara perwar-digaar aeye ya tumahray perwar-digaar ki kuch nishanain ayen ( magar ) jis roz tumahray perwar-digaar ki kuch nishanain aa jayen gi to jo shakhs pehlay imaan nahi laya hoga is waqt usay imaan lana kuch faida nahi day ga ya apne imaan ( ki haalat ) mein naik amal nahi kiye hon ge ( to gunaaho se tauba karna mufeed nah hoga ae paighambar un se ) keh do ke tum bhi intzaar karo hum bhi intzaar karte hain
  6,159,jin logon ne apne deen mein ( bohat se ) raste nikalay aur kayi kayi firqay ho gay un se tum ko kuch kaam nahi un ka kaam khuda ke hawalay phir jo kuch woh karte rahay hain woh un ko ( sab ) betaye ga
  6,160,aur jo koi ( khuda ke huzoor ) neki le kar aeye ga is ko waisi das naikian milein gi aur jo buraiee laaye ga usay saza waisay hi miley gi aur un par zulm nahikiya jaye ga
  6,161,keh do ke mujhe mere perwar-digaar ne seedha rasta dikha diya hai ( yani deen sahih ) mazhab ibrahim ka jo aik ( khuda ) hi ki taraf ke they aur mushrikon mein se nah they
  6,162,( yeh bhi ) keh do ke meri namaz aur meri ibadat aur mera jeena aur mera marna sab khuday-e rab alameen hi ke liye hai
  6,163,jis ka koi shareek nahi aur mujh ko isi baat ka hukum mila hai aur mein sab se awwal farmanbardar hon
  6,164,kahokiya mein khuda ke siwa aur perwar-digaar talaash karoon aur wohi to har cheez ka maalik hai aur jo koi ( bura ) kaam karta hai to is ka zarrar isi ko hota hai aur koi shakhs kisi ( ke gunah ) ka boojh nahi uthaye ga phir tum sab ko apne perwar-digaar ki taraf lout ka jana hai to jin jin baton mein tum ikhtilaafkiya karte they woh tum ko betaye ga
  6,165,aur wohi to hai jis ne zameen mein tum ko apna naib banaya aur aik ke dosray par darjay buland kiye taakay jo kuch is ne tumhe bakhsha hai is mein tumhari azmaish hai be shak tumhara perwar-digaar jald azaab dainay wala hai aur be shak woh bakhsnay wala meharban bhi hai
